        of the branches. Two other circulars reproduced are (1) Instruction Circular 
        No. 5572 dated 04-11-1997 which has banned creation of mortgage by certified 
        copy of title deeds and (2) Instruction Circular No. CLD:PSP:276 dated 
        07-02-1997 which has advised that the charges of equitable mortgagee may 
        be noted with the Revenue authorities. Both these circulars stand modified/relaxed 
        by the latest Instruction Circular no. 6118 dated 15-11-2000. </p> </font> <br>
